  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_160",
    "english": "Among the humans who have immigrated to the Demon Realm, they have joined the armed forces of an evil demonic cult. Slashing the enemy with a greatsword literally looks like a \"berserker\", but they have the minimum amount of reason and cooperative thoughts to attack together with the other cultists.",
